WEBVTT

00:06.734 --> 00:09.198
In New York City's war on crime,

00:09.199 --> 00:11.067
the worst criminal offenders
are pursued

00:11.068 --> 00:14.166
by the detectives
of the major case squad.

00:14.167 --> 00:16.067
These are their stories.

